title: Neenah White Index Cardstock, 300 Sheets, 110 lb/199 gsm, 94 Brightness, 8.5" x 11" - MORE SHEETS! (91635)
description: Create bold documents, brochures, coupons, invitations, reports, and more with Neenah Bright White index Cardstock. Its 110 lb weight makes it ideal for printing in inkjet and laser printers, while each sheet is lignin and acid-free to resist yellowing and disintegration over time. The smooth texture and crisp white color reproduce high resolution images and prints for attention-getting and professional documents. Choose Neenah Paper for your next project and see for yourself!
